To achieve this, you can use a `sap.m.Page` as a container for your dialog and table. When the full screen button is clicked, you can use JavaScript to toggle a CSS class that sets the table to occupy the full screen size. Here's an example code to demonstrate this:

```xml
<mvc:View
    controllerName="yourController"
    xmlns="sap.m"
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc">
