}, [isPreConfigured, baseUrl, httpClient, setConfigurationData, setWhatsAppEnabled, setwhatsAppInboundEnabled, enableSms]);
```

By using a variable isMounted within the effect function, it ensures that if the component unmounts before the fetchData function completes, the subsequent calls to setState will not trigger a state update on an unmounted component.

